data.description: This 3-story, townhome-style condo is conveniently located near the bustling heart of Virginia Beach! On the first floor, a bedroom & separate bathroom provides a relaxing opportunity for your guests. Open concept living room on the second floor seamlessly connects to a well-appointed kitchen that boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, spacious dining area, & access to your private balcony. Ascend to the third floor, where the additional bedrooms & primary suite await. The owner ensuite features a generously proportioned bedroom, walk-in closet, exquisite tray ceiling, & spa-like retreat w/dual vanities & a luxurious tile shower. Living here is a lifestyle - combining convenience, comfort, & community! Association Fees include Cox Cable, WIFI & Landline, Clubhouse, Ground maintenance, Playground, Dog park, Pool, Trash & Master Ins. Policy. Seller to pay 6 months of Condo/HOA fees with reasonable offer. Home has been virtually staged.
